Certifications: RHCSA (Red Hat Certified System Administrator) and OCA (Oracle Certified Associate).
Experience with cloud-based database services and familiarity with DevOps practices (e.g., CI/CD pipelines).
Strong understanding of High Availability (HA) and Disaster Recovery (DR) strategies for database systems.
Proficiency in database performance tuning, indexing, and partitioning to improve system performance.
Expertise in managing and troubleshooting replication technologies, including MySQL Master-Slave Replication, MySQL Group Replication, PostgreSQL Streaming Replication, and Oracle Data Guard.
Experience with Basic Docker and Container Administration, including container deployment, orchestration, and troubleshooting.